OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FITV Sport speaks to England manager
OL,7,FThomas Tuchel ahead of what is
OL,8,Fexpected to be a passionate match
OL,9,Fagainst Argentina
OL,11,FEngland manager Thomas Tuchel said he
OL,12,Fexpects a "full roller-coaster" when
OL,13,Fhis side face defending champions
OL,14,FArgentina in their World Cup semi-
OL,15,Ffinal on Wednesday, predicting an
OL,16,Femotional encounter between the two
OL,17,Frivals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
