OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FThe Three Lions are set to play just
OL,7,Ftheir fourth World Cup semi-final as
OL,8,Fthey bid to reach the final for the
OL,9,Ffirst time since 1966.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Sport, Tuchel said: "I
OL,12,Fexpect the full roller-coaster again.
OL,13,FBoth teams play too emotional, and
OL,14,Fboth teams play with too much spirit
OL,15,Fand energy to have a totally clean and
OL,16,Fcalm match."
OL,18,F"We are ready... We will be ready,"
OL,19,FTuchel corrected himself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,F"I can feel it, I can feel the
OL,7,Fexcitement of the players."
OL,9,FEngland have had a fair share of
OL,10,Fbookings during the tournament, with
OL,11,Fseven yellow cards and a red, they are
OL,12,Fthe most-booked of the semi-finalists.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Argentina have had no red
OL,14,Fcards but six yellow cards.
OL,16,FHowever, the slate will be wiped clean
OL,17,Fgoing into the semi-finals, thanks to
OL,18,FFifa's tournament amnesty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
