OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FEngland versus Argentina is one of
OL,7,Finternational football's great
OL,8,Frivalries, and winning or losing on
OL,9,FWednesday will be the difference
OL,10,Fbetween the Three Lions making the
OL,11,Ffinal of the 2026 World Cup and just
OL,12,Ffalling short.
OL,14,FSpeaking on the rivalry, Tuchel added:
OL,15,F"It's huge, it's just huge."
OL,17,F"It's two big countries, everyone
OL,18,Fknows their shirts, everyone knows
OL,19,Ftheir main players, and everyone knows
OL,20,Fwhat's at stake," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
