OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FArgentina won the last World Cup in
OL,7,F2022, and Tuchel views them as strong
OL,8,Fcompetition.
OL,10,F"They mean business," he said. "They
OL,11,Fare a tough group of players, and they
OL,12,Fhave the mentality, the winning
OL,13,Fmentality."
OL,15,FArgentina boast Lionel Messi on their
OL,16,Fside. Messi, 39, has played at six
OL,17,FWorld Cups and made 205 appearances
OL,18,Ffor his country, but the semi-final
OL,19,Fwill be his first meeting with England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
