FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FDuring the tournament so far, the star
OL,7,Fhas spent 63% of his time on the pitch
OL,8,Fwalking, according to tracking data
OL,9,Ffrom the 2026 Fifa World Cup. But
OL,10,FTuchel said this was far from a moment
OL,11,Ffor the Three Lions to "fall asleep".
OL,13,FThe England boss described Messi as a
OL,14,F"silent killer" who can "kill you
OL,15,Fwhile he's walking".
OL,17,FHe added: "You can never fall asleep,
OL,18,Fyou can never underestimate the burst
OL,19,Fof energy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,F"We have to find a way to stop it and
OL,7,Fto overcome it. We are not here to
OL,8,Fcongratulate it, or build him a
OL,9,Fthrone."
OL,11,FThe World Cup semi-final referee has
OL,12,Fproved to be a good luck charm for
OL,13,FMessi in the past.
OL,15,FAmerican official Ismael Elfath has
OL,16,Fbeen appointed to take charge of
OL,17,FWednesday's match in Atlanta, having
OL,18,Fbeen the fourth official when
OL,19,FArgentina beat France on penalties to
OL,20,Fwin the 2022 World Cup in Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784110701
OL,3,CTuchel expects 'emotional' semi-final
OL,4,Cas England take on rivals Argentina
OL,6,FElfath was the referee when Messi's
OL,7,FInter Miami team won the 2023 Leagues
OL,8,FCup and has also overseen three Major
OL,9,FLeague Soccer regular-season wins in
OL,10,Fwhich Messi has featured.
OL,12,FThe winners of Wednesday's semi-final
OL,13,Fwill take on Spain, who have made it
OL,14,Fall the way in the competition for
OL,15,Fonly the second time, to take home the
OL,16,Ftrophy.
OL,18,FIt's after Spain knocked out the
OL,19,Ftournament favourites, France, on
OL,20,FTuesday, beating them 2-0.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
